RelatedSentence: Toronto police are investigating a suspicious death after a woman was found dead at a home in downtown Toronto late Sunday night .
Toronto police and EMS responded to a call for unknown trouble at around 10:30 p.m. and found a woman 's body when they arrived on the scene .
